mpty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-58abd370994e72f25686e7549765372f_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="423" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2e718dc435225785df6733b7d99cf69b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="423" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58abd370994e72f25686e7549765372f_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-58abd370994e72f25686e7549765372f_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="423" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2e718dc435225785df6733b7d99cf69b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="423" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58abd370994e72f25686e7549765372f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-58abd370994e72f25686e7549765372f_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>面试被拒，回去与朋友开趴体庆祝失败。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e54264de2fcb4f50a9c207d4545bb936_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="424" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b18afd85c3b1848a20a0831f45c662e_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="424" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e54264de2fcb4f50a9c207d4545bb936_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-e54264de2fcb4f50a9c207d4545bb936_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="424" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b18afd85c3b1848a20a0831f45c662e_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="424" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e54264de2fcb4f50a9c207d4545bb936_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e54264de2fcb4f50a9c207d4545bb936_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>做你原来不敢做的事。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-177f9c98c878938bf9bd00bb1a929fb0_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="240" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4915a0615ac607ccfa05e9506697439_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="425" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-177f9c98c878938bf9bd00bb1a929fb0_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-177f9c98c878938bf9bd00bb1a929fb0_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="240" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4915a0615ac607ccfa05e9506697439_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="425" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-177f9c98c878938bf9bd00bb1a929fb0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-177f9c98c878938bf9bd00bb1a929fb0_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>努力忘记新车碰上的刮痕。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7471c5d0922a323918c80b313df8ee17_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="241" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-aa0179b48507a6e322f26b9dacdfb323_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="427" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7471c5d0922a323918c80b313df8ee17_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7471c5d0922a323918c80b313df8ee17_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="241" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-aa0179b48507a6e322f26b