cript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8f2b8107b67aa7385d07fd9dcccd2aad_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa8053d83e45b4b6d660bb55c191b517_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="425" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f2b8107b67aa7385d07fd9dcccd2aad_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-8f2b8107b67aa7385d07fd9dcccd2aad_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa8053d83e45b4b6d660bb55c191b517_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="425" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f2b8107b67aa7385d07fd9dcccd2aad_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8f2b8107b67aa7385d07fd9dcccd2aad_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>60岁，跑完马拉松。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b05be6eb73c69b9a051f8e8c25dda092_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="240" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cec6d683318336183f4940357237587_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="425" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b05be6eb73c69b9a051f8e8c25dda092_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-b05be6eb73c69b9a051f8e8c25dda092_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="240" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cec6d683318336183f4940357237587_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="425" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b05be6eb73c69b9a051f8e8c25dda092_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b05be6eb73c69b9a051f8e8c25dda092_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>给孙子孙女讲故事。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cc173eebc3a16321777e713a5a68ab9_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6e3d3af162c4be2613fdfb333e428db_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="425" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2cc173eebc3a16321777e713a5a68ab9_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2cc173eebc3a16321777e713a5a68ab9_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="425" data-rawheight="242" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6e3d3af162c4be2613fdfb333e428db_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="425" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2cc173eebc3a16321777e713a5a68ab9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cc173eebc3a16321777e713a5a68ab9_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>看着孩子生活如意时，自己心里满满的成就感。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-264304f74f0bb2e0d220566fa039a2d5_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="424" data-rawheight="241" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-36af8c45658e504d69a7110a7b7e96d4_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="424" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-264304f74f0bb2e0d220566fa039a2d5_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-264304f74f0bb2e0d220566fa039a2d5_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="424" data-rawheight="241" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-36af8c45658e504d69a7110a7b7e96d4_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="424" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-264304f74f0bb2e0d220566fa039a2d5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-264304f74f0bb2e0d220566fa039a2d5_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生就是……</p><p>让孙女教你操作最新款的数码产品。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f7d2294b71494d1a8d23f5beaa9f005_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="423" data-rawheight="243" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-963f6118d188b3c9419b21e51ddfa239_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="423" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9f7d2294b71494d1a8d23f5beaa9f005_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9f7d2294b71494d1a8d23f5beaa9f005_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="423" data-rawheight="243" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-963f6118d188b3c9419b21e51ddfa239_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="423" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9f7d2294b71494d1a8d23f5beaa9f005_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f7d2294b71494d1a8d23f5beaa9f005_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>人生的意义就在于——</p><p>一件件小事！</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p><b>And only little things matter because one day you’ll look back and realize that those were the big things.</b></p><p><b>那一件件小事，回过头看——原来，都是大事。         ——侵删</b></p><p><b>还有段话很喜欢的</b></p><p><b>我记得香港有个作家陶杰曾经说过：“当你老了，回顾一生，就会发觉：什么时候出国读书、什么时候决定做第一份职业、何时选定了对象而恋爱、什么时候结婚，其实都是命运的巨变。只是当时站在三岔路口，眼见风云千樯，你作出抉择的那一日，在日记上，相当沉闷和平凡，当时还以为是生命中普通的一天。”</b></p><p><b>——《杀鹌鹑的少女》</b></p><div class="RichText-MCNLinkCardContainer"><a class="MCNLinkCard" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="mcn-link-card" data-mcn-id="1218547725757075456" data-mcn-skuid="65963887569" data-mcn-source="京东" data-mcn-app-schema-android="" data-mcn-app-schema-ios="" data-za-detail-view-name="1218547725757075456" data-za-not-track-link="true" href="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=jdext-1218547725757075456-0&amp;p=AyIGZRtSFQEQAlIdWBAyFQNdHFkcCxQDUhNrUV1KWQorAlBHU0VeBUVNR0ZbSkAOClBMW0scXx0FEA5cHV8SCg1eEEcGJX5WW1R9KU5ycXUNEwdwXWlvHhwwVXIeC2UbUhUAGgZUG1wWMhIGVBtfEAERAVQraxUHIkY7G1oUBhQBVRJrFDISA1wZWRQHFwdTHl0RMhIPUSuNu5bHj%2BrC67DUuKmAluvAi7nT651rJTIRNw5OD1xHDgdWG1IRBxQBVh9dEQQTAVEeXxIeEzdVGloVChUDUBhdewN8B10YXRQEEQdSEmsVMhI3Cl8GSDIQBlQZWQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><div class="MCNLinkCard-card"><div class="MCNLinkCard-cardContainer"><div class="MCNLinkCard-imageContainer MCNLinkCard-imageContainer--square"><img class="MCNLinkCard-image" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c70b0f4e6715ac4734ed4f67da2979a4_hd.jpg" alt=""></div><div class="MCNLinkCard-info"><div class="MCNLinkCard-title"><div class="MCNLinkCard-titleText">杀鹌鹑的少女</div><div class="MCNLinkCard-tagList"><div class="MCNLinkCard-tag MCNLinkCard-tag--source">京东</div></div></div><div class="MCNLinkCard-tool"><div class="MCNLinkCard-toolLeft"><div class="MCNLinkCard-price"><span>¥ 130.00</span></div></div><div class="MCNLinkCard-button" role="button">去购买<span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center;">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowRight" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17" height="17"><path d="M9.218 16.78a.737.737 0 0 0 1.052 0l4.512-4.249a.758.758 0 0 0 0-1.063L10.27 7.22a.737.737 0 0 0-1.052 0 .759.759 0 0 0-.001 1.063L13 12l-3.782 3.716a.758.758 0 0 0 0 1.063z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></div></a></div><p><b>下次你路过,人间仍有我—</b><span><span class="UserLink"><div class="Popover"><div id="Popover34-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="Popover34-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/82736f9f1cbeb92580e0308c9ceab2de" data-za-detail-view-id="1045">@不知江月</a></div></div></span></span></p></span>'
        },
        {
          username: "第三只猫",
          avatar_url:
            "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4d7c57ced2cf4e875527ce16695d4b40_im.jpg",
          introduction: "社会心理学",

          like_count: 45362,

          content:
            '<span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemprop="text"><p>一个月前，上海世外小学两名十岁左右小学生放学路上被报复社会的人砍了数刀身亡。</p><p>上海世外作为上海最好的小学之一，遇难者妈妈当天发的朋友圈直接体现了家长的素养。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6ae8b437fc57589223a8f55176c606e_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="360" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-92e2d4ca7d02500c8521b1146998a7dd_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="440" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6ae8b437fc57589223a8f55176c606e_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f6ae8b437fc57589223a8f55176c606e_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="360" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-92e2d4ca7d02500c8521b1146998a7dd_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="440" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6ae8b437fc57589223a8f55176c606e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6ae8b437fc57589223a8f55176c606e_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>大家都在为失去两个幼小的生命悲恸的时候，他的妈妈在更加煎熬和痛苦的心情中提醒大家这个生命在短暂的十年半里给他们带来了什么。这个应该就是我们要思考的，生命虽然有限，但是它的意义是什么。</p><p>我第一次思考这个问题是小时候偷偷在游戏厅玩游戏被爸妈狠批了一顿，我在想人活着到底是为了什么。</p><p>后来在小时候看的一部动画片《大耳朵图图》第四季第24集和第25集，名字是《永远活下去》中得到了一些感触，想分享给同样思考这个问题的朋友。</p><p>在幼儿园的一个生物课堂上，有个哥哥讲到鹦鹉的平均寿命只有七年。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-36f94acc9e154b416fcf35b0557905fc_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c9f6fbb8bf6c2128b0722b3505b6418_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="534" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-36f94acc9e154b416fcf35b0557905fc_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-36f94acc9e154b416fcf35b0557905fc_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c9f6fbb8bf6c2128b0722b3505b6418_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="534" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-36f94acc9e154b416fcf35b0557905fc_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-36f94acc9e154b416fcf35b0557905fc_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>小朋友们听了之后非常的伤心。觉得七年之后鹦鹉就离开了世界。而且还联想到了自己的爸爸妈妈，这让他们更难过了。</p><p>回家之后更是茶饭不思，觉得所有人都会慢慢离开这个世界。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-562c389ca80d0363f4a1449436400df4_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="535" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-554b7d2037142f33122c13c2e6726f2c_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="535" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-562c389ca80d0363f4a1449436400df4_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-562c389ca80d0363f4a1449436400df4_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="535" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-554b7d2037142f33122c13c2e6726f2c_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="535" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-562c389ca80d0363f4a1449436400df4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-562c389ca80d0363f4a1449436400df4_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-51526d73c5c14fc0047cfd0ab257a884_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="529" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d83272e01d3e5a98c9db83285c273f6c_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="529" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-51526d73c5c14fc0047cfd0ab257a884_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-51526d73c5c14fc0047cfd0ab257a884_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="529" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d83272e01d3e5a98c9db83285c273f6c_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="529" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-51526d73c5c14fc0047cfd0ab257a884_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-51526d73c5c14fc0047cfd0ab257a884_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cc49c017c955f82a9092a124e944ac3_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="537" data-rawheight="281" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bba80e3bc6acf08dfc186e8829b614cb_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="537" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2cc49c017c955f82a9092a124e944ac3_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-2cc49c017c955f82a9092a124e944ac3_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="537" data-rawheight="281" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bba80e3bc6acf08dfc186e8829b614cb_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="537" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2cc49c017c955f82a9092a124e944ac3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cc49c017c955f82a9092a124e944ac3_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-35ce3a01d2d239d110e889bd5ddb6d87_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="535" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3994eb9b1ce1df12b9799ece959c9e80_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="535" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-35ce3a01d2d239d110e889bd5ddb6d87_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-35ce3a01d2d239d110e889bd5ddb6d87_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="535" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3994eb9b1ce1df12b9799ece959c9e80_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="535" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-35ce3a01d2d239d110e889bd5ddb6d87_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-35ce3a01d2d239d110e889bd5ddb6d87_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>后来周末，爸爸妈妈就带图图去看画展散心，希望能帮助他从不开心的情绪中走出来。</p><p>看到了毕加索的画，爸爸告诉图图：</p><p>虽然毕加索爷爷死了，离开了这个世界，但是他给这个世界留下了很多画作为礼物。</p><p>大家只要看见画就会想到毕加索爷爷，那么他的生命就永远的活在这些画里面，陪伴着我们。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3daa1906a31fb4a7094bbe95075a835_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-706e674fa5fb8f1a4a6bf98f13bb3047_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="532" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3daa1906a31fb4a7094bbe95075a835_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f3daa1906a31fb4a7094bbe95075a835_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-706e674fa5fb8f1a4a6bf98f13bb3047_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="532" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3daa1906a31fb4a7094bbe95075a835_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3daa1906a31fb4a7094bbe95075a835_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6004f47daa79b2d5902b2cf2a4611180_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8266da89aaf527ba99ecd33ce9547fbf_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="530" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6004f47daa79b2d5902b2cf2a4611180_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6004f47daa79b2d5902b2cf2a4611180_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8266da89aaf527ba99ecd33ce9547fbf_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="530" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6004f47daa79b2d5902b2cf2a4611180_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6004f47daa79b2d5902b2cf2a4611180_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-553da90361a687a8b7abcf4e4b149ea5_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="527" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b5ca72c8ffbde3d406612fd5b85119b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="527" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-553da90361a687a8b7abcf4e4b149ea5_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-553da90361a687a8b7abcf4e4b149ea5_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="527" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b5ca72c8ffbde3d406612fd5b85119b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="527" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-553da90361a687a8b7abcf4e4b149ea5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-553da90361a687a8b7abcf4e4b149ea5_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec1107af28c55aade2a46b8a4bc3dce9_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="531" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb6202e75e2a2a9dac8c37fea0bc3bc8_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="531" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ec1107af28c55aade2a46b8a4bc3dce9_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ec1107af28c55aade2a46b8a4bc3dce9_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="531" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb6202e75e2a2a9dac8c37fea0bc3bc8_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="531" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ec1107af28c55aade2a46b8a4bc3dce9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec1107af28c55aade2a46b8a4bc3dce9_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>后来下午一家人去公园草地上玩。图图看见一片树叶枯萎掉下了，就问爸爸“它死掉了吗？”</p><p>爸爸跟他说：</p><p>它表面上看起来是死了，但是它会化作肥料，变成大树的营养物质，明年大树就能长出很多新的树叶来，这个就是这片树叶留个这个世界的礼物。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-65b58764a0cbd0fdc0cfabcc76348472_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-799209bf44c1bb74aaf187ee676082db_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="530" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65b58764a0cbd0fdc0cfabcc76348472_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-65b58764a0cbd0fdc0cfabcc76348472_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-799209bf44c1bb74aaf187ee676082db_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="530" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65b58764a0cbd0fdc0cfabcc76348472_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-65b58764a0cbd0fdc0cfabcc76348472_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-165fa3b6534b12aee393936ee129cb63_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f47f05089a807201089b37dc9bce6aa_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="532" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-165fa3b6534b12aee393936ee129cb63_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-165fa3b6534b12aee393936ee129cb63_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f47f05089a807201089b37dc9bce6aa_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="532" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-165fa3b6534b12aee393936ee129cb63_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-165fa3b6534b12aee393936ee129cb63_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8e10ada91d486c343391510b81f11b4_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b0798088d5af0b88ba09b14c5f944924_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="530" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e8e10ada91d486c343391510b81f11b4_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-e8e10ada91d486c343391510b81f11b4_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="276" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b0798088d5af0b88ba09b14c5f944924_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="530" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e8e10ada91d486c343391510b81f11b4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8e10ada91d486c343391510b81f11b4_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0a289e3b0c88cb5be51e0bbf44dd1c84_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="531" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-35f067d298ced62a326363622cd20f5d_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="531" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0a289e3b0c88cb5be51e0bbf44dd1c84_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0a289e3b0c88cb5be51e0bbf44dd1c84_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="531" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-35f067d298ced62a326363622cd20f5d_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="531" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0a289e3b0c88cb5be51e0bbf44dd1c84_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0a289e3b0c88cb5be51e0bbf44dd1c84_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>图图后来想到了自己的爸爸妈妈不是画家，也不是音乐家，他们又能给这个世界留下什么礼物呢？</p><p>爸爸妈妈告诉他：他们留下礼物很多，其中最大的礼物就是图图，送给了这个世界一个可爱的孩子。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d716a182b9d8ed2e1ea25bdd9f372b16_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-af4252e2da839f1f9a0df6feec332009_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="532" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d716a182b9d8ed2e1ea25bdd9f372b16_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d716a182b9d8ed2e1ea25bdd9f372b16_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="532" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-af4252e2da839f1f9a0df6feec332009_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="532" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d716a182b9d8ed2e1ea25bdd9f372b16_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d716a182b9d8ed2e1ea25bdd9f372b16_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f860567d8a9ae005f94103506e57421_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="526" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1da6724c7d2d7e480c00aa43fabeb1f3_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="526" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9f860567d8a9ae005f94103506e57421_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-9f860567d8a9ae005f94103506e57421_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="526" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1da6724c7d2d7e480c00aa43fabeb1f3_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="526" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9f860567d8a9ae005f94103506e57421_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f860567d8a9ae005f94103506e57421_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0587b6610777185d562345bd2e640ba2_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="527" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-159d9dc70b5163dc0e6b1e77bb419363_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="527" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0587b6610777185d562345bd2e640ba2_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-0587b6610777185d562345bd2e640ba2_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="527" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-159d9dc70b5163dc0e6b1e77bb419363_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="527" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0587b6610777185d562345bd2e640ba2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0587b6610777185d562345bd2e640ba2_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a926585abf02c17c5ff502af9d032bb_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="525" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-31d3f995e656b1b43088e4d54c90be4b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="525" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9a926585abf02c17c5ff502af9d032bb_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-9a926585abf02c17c5ff502af9d032bb_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="525" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-31d3f995e656b1b43088e4d54c90be4b_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="525" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9a926585abf02c17c5ff502af9d032bb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a926585abf02c17c5ff502af9d032bb_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>所以图图后来明白了：</p><p><b>人活着，生命的意义就是不断的给这个世界留下礼物，这样我们就能永远的活下去，活在我们留下的礼物里</b>。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7088787ba3730b174e92494746fcb06_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="524" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-00df3ba849848c2f8b66a849055ab503_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="524" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f7088787ba3730b174e92494746fcb06_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f7088787ba3730b174e92494746fcb06_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="524" data-rawheight="277" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-00df3ba849848c2f8b66a849055ab503_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="524" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f7088787ba3730b174e92494746fcb06_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7088787ba3730b174e92494746fcb06_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2063d3ba607164a1a8995fb206353bcf_hd.jpg" data-rawwidth="528" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a64e216e7e84b8bb47a4817f79e2efef_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="528" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2063d3ba607164a1a8995fb206353bcf_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2063d3ba607164a1a8995fb206353bcf_720w.jpg" data-rawwidth="528" data-rawheight="278" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a64e216e7e84b8bb47a4817f79e2efef_hd.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="528" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2063d3ba607164a1a8995fb206353bcf_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2063d3ba607164a1a8995fb206353bcf_hd.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"></figure><p>生命的意义从动画片小孩子口中说出来，更让人触动。对的，所有人都要死，但是我们要给这个世界留下点好的东西，留下“礼物”，让那些活着的人因为我们曾留下的这些东西而时常想起着我们，这样，我们看起来死了，但是或许能永远的活在那些“礼物”中。</p></span>'
        }
      ]
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    this.requestQuestion();
    //初始化回答列表
    this.requestAnswer(this.page_num);

    // 增加监听页面滑动事件
    window.addEventListener("scroll", this.handleScroll);
  },
  methods: {
    requestQuestion() {
      this.questionId = this.$route.params["questionId"];
      // console.log(this.questionId);

      this.$axios
        .get("/question/" + this.questionId, {
          headers: {
            Authorization: localStorage.getItem("token")
          }
        })
        .then(res => {
          // console.log(res.data);
          this.question = res.data.data;
        })
        .catch(e => {
          this.errors.push(e);
        });
    },
    requestAnswer(page_num) {
      this.$axios
        .get(
          "/question/" + this.questionId + "/answers?currentPage=" + page_num,
          {
            headers: {
              Authorization: localStorage.getItem("token")
            }
          }
        )
        .then(res => {
          // console.log(res.data);
          this.total_page_num = res.data.data.pages;
          this.num_per_page = res.data.data.size;
          this.total_answer_num = res.data.data.total;

          this.new_answer = res.data.data.records;
          this.answer_list = this.answer_list.concat(this.new_answer);
        })
        .catch(e => {
          this.errors.push(e);
        });
    },
    nextAnswer(index) {
      let target = "#ans" + index;
      if (target == "#ans" + this.answer_list.length) {
        target = "#bottom";
      }
      let options = {};

      this.$vuetify.goTo(target, options);
      // $vuetify.goTo(target, options);
    },
    gotoHello() {
      this.$vuetify.goTo("#hello", {});
    },
    handleScroll() {
      //变量scrollTop是滚动条滚动时,距离顶部的距离
      let scrollTop =
        document.documentElement.scrollTop || document.body.scrollTop;
      //变量windowHeight是可视区的高度
      let windowHeight =
        document.documentElement.clientHeight || document.body.clientHeight;
      //变量scrollHeight是滚动条的总高度
      let scrollHeight =
        document.documentElement.scrollHeight || document.body.scrollHeight;

      if (scrollTop + windowHeight >= scrollHeight - 10) {
        if (this.page_num < this.total_page_num) {
          // this.show_progress = true;
          this.page_num++;
          this.requestAnswer(this.page_num);
        } else {
          // this.show_progress = false;
        }
      } else {
        // this.show_progress = false;
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>

